    <item>
      <title>What is Relationship?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/what-is-relationship/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/what-is-relationship/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5260-what-is-relationship.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;What is Relationships&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;What is Relationships? 
    &lt;div id=&#34;what-is-relationships&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#what-is-relationships&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When I was in school, one of my friends had a father who was a very wealthy business tycoon. After my friend turned 18, his father took him to a bank and asked the bank officers to open an account for him.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One day, I needed some money, and my friend somehow knew that my poor parents couldn’t easily come up with that amount. To help me, he went to the bank and asked the banker for money, saying that he had a bank account there.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>What is Relationship - Poem</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/what-is-relationship-poem/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/wiaposts/what-is-relationship-poem/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5260-what-is-relationship.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;What is Relationships - Poem&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;What is Relationships - Poem 
    &lt;div id=&#34;what-is-relationships---poem&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#what-is-relationships---poem&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In school, a friend with wealth so grand,&lt;br&gt;
His father took him by the hand,&lt;br&gt;
To the bank, where an account was made,&lt;br&gt;
A fortune&amp;rsquo;s future, it seemed, was laid.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One day, I needed money fast,&lt;br&gt;
My friend knew my parents couldn&amp;rsquo;t amass,&lt;br&gt;
He hurried to the bank to plead,&lt;br&gt;
But found his riches couldn’t meet the need.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
